{
  "texts": [
    "However, this approach is primarily tailored to GPT-2 prompts and our evaluation indicates that it does not generalize well to GPT-3 models.",
    "In another study, the authors in [59] utilized a transformer similar to the one employed in GPT-2 to create a tool called Grover.",
    "Grover is capable of generating text such as fake news and is also able to detect its own generated text.",
    "The study demonstrated the effectiveness of Grover in verifying self-generated fake news.",
    "Nevertheless, it remains uncertain how well Grover would perform on text generated by other GPT models."
  ]
}